# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Node
node_modules/

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/

# Office lock files
.~lock.*

# Temporary files generated during PDF conversion
*.tmp
```

Quick way to create it from Git Bash:

```bash
cat > .gitignore << 'EOF'
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
.ipynb_checkpoints/
node_modules/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
.~lock.*
*.tmp
EOF